            paragraph5: 'TSH-200 single shaft solid waste shredder minimizes operating costs with special blade design and smart load management offering energy efficiency. Ideal investment for metropolitan municipal integrated waste management projects, international recycling consortiums, free zone waste processing centers and environmental organization large-scale projects. Requires minimum maintenance with automatic lubrication system, reinforced bearing structure, industrial cooling system and solid steel body. Supported by all global safety standards (CE, UL, ISO 9001, ISO 14001, ISO 45001) and 5-year platinum warranty.',
            paragraph6: 'TSH-200 providing sustainability in waste management offers high efficiency, environmental benefits and economic advantages to businesses by optimizing recycling processes. MT Makina, Turkey\'s leading shredder manufacturer, offers single shaft solid waste shredder price quotes, turnkey project solutions, 24/7 global technical support and on-site maintenance service. Contact our professional consultancy team for your plastic shredder, fabric shredder, pallet shredder and paper shredder needs. TSH-200 is the top-class shredding solution recommended for mega-scale industrial projects, international recycling complexes and turnkey projects requiring maximum capacity.'
